nodes.text: A countess lived on Abregado-rae during the High Republic Era. She ordered a saberfish from Tibrin for her private aquarium, which was transported onboard the freighter Legacy Run. When the fish grew sick and the countess' people did not know how to care for it, she paid for the Run to transport it back to Tibrin, which the starship's captain, Hedda Casset, thought well of her for.
